title: 20 - Shalewa Sharpe
itunes:title: 20 - Shalewa Sharpe
description: Oooh, this story is so good! Coming atcha this week is the fabulous Shalewa Sharpe. You know her from HBO’s “2 Dope Queens,” Comedy Central’s “The New Negroes,” and her own hilarious albums Stay Eating Cookies and So You Just Out Here? We’re chatting about small town weirdos, representing where you come from, the South vs. the North, and pitbulls. Here’s five words to describe this episode: get friendly with your neighbors.
